::Fenox::

Fenox looked at D for a while, her eyes flat. She finally shook her 
head.

"I know he's not good, you silly wolf!" she exclaimed, not sure 
whether to be mad for him making her get away from being able to 
monitor Vlad or to be greatful that he cared enough about the 
situation to tell her, "I was monitoring him back there. Now is that 
all?"
